2.2 You're not allowed to change the app in any way.
User Conduct and Safety
3.1 You agree to use Outside only for lawful purposes and in a way that doesn't break any laws or hurt anyone else's rights. Bullying, harassment, and other illegal or harmful behavior is not allowed.
3.2 If Outside sees that you're breaking the rules, or if another user reports behavior that violates these rules, we can take action such as giving you a warning, suspending your account, or permanently banning you from using the app.
3.3 You're responsible for your own conduct and any content you share on the app. You're not allowed to share anything on the app that could harm other people or devices.
3.4 You agree to follow all laws and regulations related to data protection, privacy, and user safety. Also, You agree to provide accurate information when you sign up for an account.
